# 
def out2(row):
    out = 0
    for feature in log_data.keys():
        p = row[feature]
        f = log_data[feature]
        # TODOQ125th
        Q1 = np.percentile(f,25)
    
        # TODOQ375th
        Q3 = np.percentile(f,75)
    
        # TODO1.5
        step = 1.5*(Q3-Q1)
        if (p <= Q1 - step) or (p >= Q3 + step): 
            out += 1
    return out > 1 
## 
lst = []
for i,row in log_data.iterrows():
    if out2(row): 
        lst.append(i)
display(log_data.ix[lst])
